n bypass to add payment data without administrator notice. Shopify resolved this issue by applying the authorization check on that function","can_view?":true,"can_edit?":false,"content_html":"\u003cp\u003eUsing this vulnerability a User with limited access/ No access to Settings could add/alter/change Payment settings while having disallowed by the Administrator.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt was possible to use this Authorization bypass to add payment data without administrator notice. Shopify resolved this issue by applying the authorization check on that function\u003c/p\u003e\n"}]}